race.comment: CELTIC ROSE (3) resumed and showed more like her best when beaten 1L over 1100m at this track. She led in that and draws the paint today. Nicely placed to go one better. OXIDIZE (7) resumes and owns a Longford trial win. Her Hobart form stacks right up and she has to be kept very safe. PARTY DAY (8) turned in a much better run at her second appearance missing by 1.3L over 1009m at Devonport Synthetic. Can improve further and should be in the finish. LA ZAMPA (1) was in the money at Devonport Synthetic first up but was plainer here following well supported. Has a low gate and the top rider is reunited. A much better effort is likely.
